9 AS INTRODUCED
10 An Act relating to notaries; amending 49 O.S. 2021,
Section 1.1, which relates to notary commission
11 applications; removing home address requirement; and
providing an effective date.
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 49 O.S. 2021, Section 1.1, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 1.1. The application for a notary commission shall set
18 forth:
19 1. The name of the applicant, printed exactly as the applicant
20 will sign documents as a notary public;
21 2. Former names of the applicant, if any;
22 3. If a resident of this state, the county of residence and
23 street address of the applicant;
24
