BOLD FACE denotes Committee Amendments.

1 4. If a resident of another state, the county and street
2 address of the applicant's place of employment in Oklahoma and the
3 applicant's residence address;
4 5. 4. Daytime phone number of the applicant;
5 6. 5. Electronic mail address of the applicant;
6 7. 6. A statement that the applicant is at least eighteen (18)
7 years of age;
8 8. 7. A designation of new, renewal, or expired commission
9 including an expiration date if applicable;
10 9. 8. A statement that the applicant is a citizen of the United
11 States;
12 10. 9. A statement that the applicant has never been convicted
13 of a felony;
14 11. 10. A statement that the applicant is able to read and
15 write in English; and
16 12. 11. Signature of the applicant, exactly as the applicant
17 will sign documents as a notary public.
18 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
19
